---
import DocLayout from '../../../layouts/DocLayout.astro';
---
<DocLayout
  title="agentmako recipes — practical agent workflows · agentmako"
  description="Practical recipes for AI coding agents using agentmako. Trace auth, refactor safely, edit databases with schema awareness, debug tricky bugs."
  canonicalPath="/docs/recipes/"
  ogImage="/assets/og.png"
  ogType="website"
  breadcrumbs={[{"name": "Home", "href": "/"}, {"name": "Docs", "href": "/docs/"}, {"name": "Recipes", "href": "/docs/recipes/"}]}
>
<header class="doc-page-header">
  <span class="eyebrow">Recipes</span>
    <h1 style="margin-top:1rem;">agentmako <em>recipes</em></h1>
    <p class="doc-hero__sub">
      <strong>agentmako</strong> is a local-first MCP server for AI
      coding agents. The recipes below are practical walkthroughs of the
      common workflows: trace an auth flow, refactor safely, edit a
      Postgres / Supabase schema with full awareness of the call sites,
      debug a vague bug without grep loops.
    </p>
</header>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="agents" style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <a class="agent-card" href="./auth-flow-tracing.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Trace an auth flow</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Recipe</span><span>auth_path</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          Walk a route to its handler, find the RLS, fix the bug —
          without grepping the codebase first.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./safe-refactoring.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Refactor safely</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Recipe</span><span>imports_impact</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          Rename an exported function across a real codebase without
          shipping broken callers.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./database-aware-edits.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Schema-aware edits</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Recipe</span><span>db_table_schema</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          Add a Postgres column with RLS, find every code site that
          touches the table, audit tenant isolation.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./debugging-with-context.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Debug with context</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Recipe</span><span>context_packet</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          A real "hydration error" debug session — start from
          <code>context_packet</code>, narrow with freshness, fix.
        </p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</DocLayout>
